Description_lang: Consume Magic generates $278326s2 Fury when a beneficial Magic effect is successfully removed from the target.

description_blz.en_US: Consume Magic generates 20 Fury when a beneficial Magic effect is successfully removed from the target.
description_blz.es_MX: Consumir magia genera 20 p. de furia cuando se elimina un efecto mágico beneficioso del objetivo.
description_blz.pt_BR: Consumir Magia gera 20 de Fúria quando remove um efeito benéfico do alvo.
description_blz.de_DE: Wenn 'Magie aufzehren' erfolgreich einen nützlichen magischen Effekt vom Ziel entfernt, werden 20 Jähzorn erzeugt.
description_blz.en_GB: Consume Magic generates 20 Fury when a beneficial Magic effect is successfully removed from the target.

description_blz.ru_RU: При успешном снятии с цели благотворного магического эффекта "Поглощение магии" дает 20 ед. гнева.
description_blz.ko_KR: 마법 삼키기로 대상의 이로운 마법 효과를 성공적으로 제거하면 20의 격노를 생성합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 吞噬魔法會在成功移除目標身上的增益魔法效果後產生20點魔怒。
description_blz.zh_CN: 从目标身上成功移除增益魔法时，吞噬魔法会产生20点恶魔之怒。
